{"type":"message","id":"f37776d6","parentId":"fecb0246","timestamp":"2026-03-19T10:02:27.442Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:5071638d-65c3-4709-a509-3fddb9b5a2d6 May: 系统健康检查] 你是 May（核心主控），执行系统健康检查：\n1. 检查 OpenClaw Gateway 状态\n2. 检查已安装技能状态\n3. 检查磁盘空间和系统资源\n4. 生成简明的健康报告发送给用户\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 18:02 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 10:02 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773914547441}}
